race.description: Aceit Transport Solutions C,G & E Handicap (Bm62)
race.comment: THREATENING (3) has made a very good impression since arriving in SA and looks well placed to win again. He's shown a sharp turn of foot at both recent runs, including last start where he got back to near last and rattled home late to run third. He draws well and drops back to 1200m here. If he's within striking distance, he's the horse to beat. THERE GOES MY HERO (2) got back and ran home very well first-up. His second-up record is brilliant so he must go into calculations. TOTTORI (10) could be ready to peak after a couple of runs back from a long spell, while ROB THE BANK (1) is a last-start winner that looks a chance to continue his winning rise.
